    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not just a break though. i mean, a break implies you're coming back to something. but what if the well is actually dry? what if the \"beauty\" you're talking about was just a temporary fluke and now i'm just an empty shell taking up space? it feels more like i'm just a ghost haunting my own life, waiting for the inevitable. it feels almost more respectful to the work i did to just... stop, rather than dragging out this hollowed-out version of myself.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
